        "category": "summary",
        "text": "Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to manipulate information on the affected products.",
        "title": "Risk evaluation"
      },
      {
        "category": "other",
        "text": "Critical Manufacturing, Energy, Food and Agriculture",
